y roles including leadership of president obamas transition teams review of international lending agencies and his service as an economic advisor to governments in developing and emerging markets have given him valuable insights and perspectives on international business and financial services dr henry brings to the board extensive experience in executive leadership at a large private university including a robust understanding of the issues facing companies and governments in both mature and emerging markets around the world primary qualifications consumer business and financial services corporate governance financial reporting international business or economics  dr henry has announced his intention to step down as dean of the leonard n stern school of business at the end of  source citigroup inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view peter b henry phds full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like peter b henry phd more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in peter b henry phds network and community follow changes in peter b henry phds employment and moneyinmotion connect with peter b henry phd through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example peter b henry phd peter b henry phds connections  sign up now to view peter b henry phds  connections » john t cahill board member the kraft heinz company jeanne p jackson president product and merchandising nike inc james e rohr lead independent director eqt corporation susan hockfield board member general electric company marijn e dekkers board member general electric company risa j lavizzomourey board member hess corporation sebastien m bazin board member general electric company ernesto zedillo ponce de leon board member the procter  gamble company elizabeth j comstock vice chairman chief executive officer business innovations general electric company gary m reiner